704124f-b.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - 28th Street (East)
704124f-b.text:
(1)  2806 Emmons Ave., south side, east from East 28th Street. The
frame house in the foreground, is now the Varuna Boat Club, formerly
a private estate.
July 13, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, from another angle.
July 13, 1933.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
